Modify code and change version in setup.py

  # version='1.0'
  vim setup.py

Create distribution package:

  python setup.py sdist

Test install:

  sudo python install dist/ksmtp-1.0.tar.gz

Remove Test install:

 sudo pip uninstall ksmtp

Configure PyPI:

  # ~/.pypirc
  python setup.py register

Upload project:

  python setup.py sdist upload

Install project:

 pip install --upgrade ksmtp

